    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche buns</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove <strong>leaves</strong> from the <strong>lettuce </strong>for 1 per person<strong> </strong>and set aside</p><p>Chop the<strong> inner core</strong> into quarters, lengthways – these are your <strong>lettuce wedges</strong></p>",
