      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated paneer </strong>and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden and crisp – this is your <strong>crispy spiced paneer</strong></p><p>Spread <strong>mango chutney</strong> over each<strong> toasted brioche lid</strong></p>",
