    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, top each <strong>toasted brioche base</strong> with a<strong> reserved lettuce leaf</strong>, the <strong>crispy spiced paneer</strong>,<strong> </strong>a dollop of the<strong> mint yoghurt</strong>,<strong> </strong>some<strong> quick-pickled onion </strong>and a<strong> toasted brioche lid </strong>– these are your<strong> crispy spiced paneer burgers</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sweet potato fries</strong> and <strong>lettuce wedges</strong> to the side, then spoon the <strong>remaining quick-pickled onion </strong>and<strong> mint yoghurt </strong>over the lettuce wedges</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
